item.title: CVE-2020-5594|2024-08-04T08:30:24.558Z -- mitsubishi%20electric%20corporation -- melsec%20iq-r%2C%20iq-f%2C%20q%2C%20l%2C%20and%20fx%20series%20cpu%20modules
item.description: Mitsubishi Electric MELSEC iQ-R, iQ-F, Q, L, and FX series CPU modules all versions contain a vulnerability that allows cleartext transmission of sensitive information between CPU modules and GX Works3 and/or GX Works2 via unspecified vectors.
